---
// Services Section based on crawled 10botics.com data
// This was originally Elementor call-to-action widgets
---

<section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
        到校服務
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        為學校提供專業的 STEM 教育服務，讓學生在實踐中學習
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- STEM Courses -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
        <div class="h-48 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-blue-700 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-16 h-16 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">STEM 課程</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            專業的 STEM 課程設計，涵蓋科學、技術、工程和數學，讓學生全面發展。
          </p>
          <a href="/stem-courses-landing-page" class="inline-flex items-center text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700 font-semibold">
            了解更多
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- STEM Day -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
        <div class="h-48 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-500 to-green-700 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-16 h-16 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">STEM Day</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            舉辦 STEM 主題日活動，讓學生在輕鬆愉快的氛圍中體驗科學的樂趣。
          </p>
          <a href="/stemday" class="inline-flex items-center text-green-600 hover:text-green-700 font-semibold">
            了解更多
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- AI Courses -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
        <div class="h-48 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500 to-purple-700 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-16 h-16 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.75 17L9 20l-1 1h8l-1-1-.75-3M3 13h18M5 17h14a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">AI 人工智能課程</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            專門的人工智能課程，讓學生了解 AI 的基本概念和實際應用。
          </p>
          <a href="/school-courses/ai-courses" class="inline-flex items-center text-purple-600 hover:text-purple-700 font-semibold">
            了解更多
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Teacher Workshop -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
        <div class="h-48 bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-500 to-orange-700 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-16 h-16 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.746 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.246 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">教師工作坊</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            為教師提供專業培訓，提升 STEM 教學能力，掌握最新的教育方法。
          </p>
          <a href="/teacher-workshop" class="inline-flex items-center text-orange-600 hover:text-orange-700 font-semibold">
            了解更多
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Contact Us -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
        <div class="h-48 bg-gradient-to-br from-red-500 to-red-700 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-16 h-16 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 4.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">聯絡我們</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            想了解更多關於我們的服務？歡迎聯絡我們，我們會為您提供專業建議。
          </p>
          <a href="/contact-us" class="inline-flex items-center text-red-600 hover:text-red-700 font-semibold">
            了解更多
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Funding Application -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
        <div class="h-48 bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-500 to-indigo-700 flex items-center justify-center">
          <svg class="w-16 h-16 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">資助申請</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            協助學校申請各類教育資助，包括「IT創新實驗室」等政府資助計劃。
          </p>
          <a href="/funding-application/it-innovation-lab" class="inline-flex items-center text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-700 font-semibold">
            了解更多
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section> 